message.content: As a language model AI developed by OpenAI, I am afraid that my official publication date is not available. However, GPT-3 was officially introduced on June 11th, 2020 in a research paper titled "Language Models are Few-Shot Learners", which was published on the arXiv preprint server. If you want to consider this as an important event related to me, then it can be regarded as my birthday.
